{"title": "Covering China\u2019s party congress in a time of Covid-19", "tags": "asia", "timestamp": "2022-10-20", "content": "BEIJING \u2013 During what is arguably the most important work week for reporters in China for at least the past decade, my colleagues and I have been badly hit by the capital city\u2019s Covid-19 measures.\nI\u2019m not just talking about the swab tests we have been taking at least once every three days, if not daily, but also the door-to-door testing and, worse, flash lockdowns."}